Compare the debate over digital (in)sentience.
(I'm not sure of the solution, just noting the problem)

@Rob_Chipman @StijnBruers @KSAfricaHack @JoshuaHiles @herbivorize @PaulDolman3 @SteveCJjones @StephenCorrySvl @Alexander_Lees @AmiesPhilip Our overriding priority should be getting factory-farms and slaughterhouses shut and outlawed (don't read / watch the below if you already agree)
https://t.co/PgfsU7yh2R
