Not merely is there no oasis - you don’t experience a mirage either!  
I reckon this is a step too far…

@peterwildeford How should you respond if you learn that a friend or colleague once said something totally out-of-character? 
My jaw dropped - until I read  https://t.co/eKH5jOn33q
Ah. Last century we had many lively discussions, but NB isn't a racist - then or now.

